0Cricket%20Board%20(PCB).%20Kaneria%2C%20who%20played%2061%20Tests%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20called%20out%20the%20PCB%20for%20the%20backbiting%20culture%20in%20Pakistan%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20taken%20for%20granted%3B%20that's%20why%20the%20downfall%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket%20has%20gone%20through%20making%20captains%2C%20changing%20captain.%20That%20will%20not%20work.%20Stick%20to%20your%20captain%20stick%20with%20him.%20Okay%2C%20I%20have%20made%20him%20the%20captain%20for%20one%20year.%20I%20will%20ask%20him.%20I%20will%20ask%20him%20to%20give%20me%20an%20answer%20after%20one%20year.%20Nobody%20will%20touch%20him%20you%20have%20full%20support%20from%20me%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20perform.%20If%20you%20don't%20perform%2C%20you%20go%20out%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20thing%20you%20have%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions.%20Why%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20make%20tough%20decisions%2C%20things%20will%20not%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaneria%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeVQI8GG3R7w%5C%22%3ERepublic%20TV.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Kaneria%20hailed%20Indian%20cricket%20for%20creating%20an%20environment%20of%20smooth%20transition%20whenever%20there's%20a%20change%20in%20guard.%20Kaneria%20also%20praised%20current%20India%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20oozing%20positive%20attitude%20and%20strong%20personality%2C%20something%20which%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20lacking%20in%20its%20recent%20coaching%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20today%20other%20teams%20are%20doing%20so%20well%20Why%20is%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%20doing%20so%20well%3F%20They%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20w