ring%20his%20recent%20visits%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fop79fk94_pm-modi-putin-zelenskyy-modi-russia-ukraine_625x300_08_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20received%20warmly%20both%20by%20Putin%20and%20Zelenskyy%20during%20his%20recent%20visits%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20talks%20with%20Mr%20Zelensky%20that%20took%20place%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20India%20is%20ever%20ready%20to%20play%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%20role%26quot%3B%20in%20every%20effort%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20he%20would%20even%20like%20to%20contribute%20personally%20in%20ending%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20who%20had%20already%20visited%20Russia%20earlier%2C%20followed%20up%20his%20Ukraine%20visit%20with%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20President%20Putin.%20%26quot%3BSpoke%20with%20President%20Putin%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20written%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X%20on%20August%2027%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20%26quot%3BExchanged%20perspectives%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20and%20my%20insights%20from%20the%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ukraine.%20Reiterated%20India's%20firm%20commitment%20to%20support%20an%20early%2C%20abiding%20and%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Speaks%20With%20Russian%20President%20Putin%20After%20His%20Visit%20To%20Ukraine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fsite%3Dclassic%26id%3D830562%26autostart%3Dfalse%26autoplay%3D0%26pWidth%3D500%26pHeight%3D281%26category%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20Office%20in%20the%20joint%20India-Ukrai