%20To%20Gold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Navdeep%20Singh's%20silver%20medal%20was%20upgraded%20to%20gold%20after%20initial%20winner%20Iran's%20Sadegh%20Beit%20Sayah%20was%20disqualified%20for%20repeatedly%20displaying%20an%20objectionable%20flag%20following%20a%20dramatic%20men's%20javelin%20throw%20F41%20final%20at%20the%20Paris%20Paralympics%20on%20Saturday.%20This%20is%20India's%20first-ever%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20men's%20javelin%20F41%20category.%20The%2023-year-old%20para-athlete%20from%20Haryana%2C%20who%20had%20finished%20fourth%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Games%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20produced%20a%20personal%20best%20effort%20of%2047.32m%20to%20claim%20the%20top%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavdeep%2C%20who%20competes%20in%20the%20classification%20meant%20for%20athletes%20of%20short%20stature%2C%20originally%20ended%20with%20a%20silver%20after%20he%20upstaged%20world%20record%20holder%20Sun%20Pengxiang%20of%20China%20with%20a%2047.32m%20throw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20was%20upgraded%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20gold%20after%20Sadegh's%20disqualification.%20Pengxiang%20(44.72m)%20finished%20with%20a%20silver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayah%20had%20managed%20to%20nose%20ahead%20of%20the%20field%20with%20a%20new%20Paralympic%20record%20of%2047.64m%20in%20his%20penultimate%20throw%20but%20lost%20the%20medal%20owing%20to%20his%20antics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhy%20to%20need%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIranian%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Iranian%3C%2Fa%3E%20Beit%20Sayah%20Sadegh's%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhere%20is%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKyUF8lI6e7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKyUF8lI6e7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anil%20Bansal%20(%40dilseanilbansal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdilseanilbansal%2Fstatus%2F1832501378654093603%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Paralympic%20Committee%20rules%20bar%20athletes%20from%20making%20any%20political%20gestures%20at%20the%20event%20and%20Sayah%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20final%20results%20for%20unsporting%2Fimproper%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIraq's%20Nukhailawi%20Wildan%20(40.46)%20claimed%20the%20bronze%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20the%20competition%20with%20a%20foul%2C%20Navdeep%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20event%20with%20a%20personal%20best%20of%2044.29%20metres%20and%20a%20season%20best%20of%2042.82%20metres%2C%20came%20up%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2046.39%20metres%20in%20his%20second%20attempt%2C%20propelling%20him%20to%20the%20second%20place.%20But%20it%20was%20his%20third%20throw%20that%20electrified%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20monstrous%20throw%20of%2047.32%20metres%2C%20Navdeep%20shattered%20the%20Paralympic%20record%20and%20surged%20into%20lead%2C%20only%20for%20Sadegh%20to%20better%20the%20Indian's%20mark%20with%20an%20effort%20of%2047.64%20metres%20in%20his%20fifth%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavdeep's%20Journey%3A%20From%20adversity%20to%20international%20podium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Panipat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Navdeep%20faced%20challenges%20from%20the%20start%20but%20he%20refused%20to%20let%20his%20condition%20define%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20his%20father%2C%20a%20national-level%20wrestler%20and%20Gram%20Sachiv%2C%20Navdeep%20channelled%20his%20passion%20into%20athletics%2C%20overcoming%20societal%20expectations%20and%20physical%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20education%20at%20Unique%20Public%20School%20and%20earning%20a%20B.A.%20in%20Hindi%20(Hons.)%20from%20Delhi%20University%2C%20Navdeep's%20commitment%20to%20sports%20only%20grew%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20took%20a%20decisive%20turn%20in%202017%2C%20when%20he%20began%20professional%20coaching%20and%20made%20his%20international%20debut%20at%20the%20Asian%20Youth%20Para%20Games%2C%20where%20he%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20javelin%20throw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20proving%20that%20his%20determination%20and%20grit%20could%20overcome%20any%20challenge.%20Navdeep%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20five%20national%20gold%20medals%20and%20secured%20an%20international%20gold%20at%20the%202021%20Fazza%20International%20Championship%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20setbacks%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Paralympics%20and%20the%20Asian%20Para%20Games%20in%202022%2C%20where%20he%20finished%20fourth%2C%20Navdeep%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20an%20inspector%20in%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20rebounded%20by%20earning%20bronze%20at%20the%20World%20Para%20Athletics%20Championships%20in%20Kobe%2C%20Japan%2C%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725777960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F1d5th8b8_navdeep-singh-and-sadegh-beit-sayah_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fparalympic-games-2024%2Fhow-flag-controversy-saw-indias-navdeep-singh-clinch-javelin-throw-f41-gold-medal-in-paralympics-6514618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Navdeep%2C%20who%20competes%20in%20the%20classification%20meant%20for%20athletes%20of%20short%20stature%2C%20originally%20ended%20with%20a%20silver%20after%20he%20upstaged%20world%20record%20holder%20Sun%20Pengxiang%20of%20China%20with%20a%2047.32m%20throw.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Nightbitch%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Amy%2