ince%20Harry%20was%20recently%20spotted%20attending%20the%20funeral%20of%20Lord%20Robert%20Fellowes%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20Lady%20Jane%20Fellowes%2C%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%26quot%3B%20stayed%20with%20his%20uncle%20Charles%20Spencer%20at%20Althorp%20House%2C%20the%20childhood%20home%20of%20Princess%20Diana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spencer%20family%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20support%20for%20Harry%2C%20who%20has%20faced%20scrutiny%20and%20criticism%20since%20stepping%20back%20from%20royal%20duties.%20His%20late%20mother%2C%20Princess%20Diana%2C%20was%20laid%20to%20rest%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20Althorp%20House%2C%20which%20holds%20sentimental%20value%20for%20Harry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20comes%20as%20Prince%20Harry's%20relationship%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20Prince%20William%2C%20and%20father%2C%20King%20Charles%2C%20remains%20tense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20much%20better%20that%20Harry%20has%20some%20links%20with%20his%20UK%20family%2C%20even%20if%20reconciliation%20with%20the%20Windsor%20side%20may%20be%20a%20long%20way%20off%2C%20if%20indeed%20it%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20royal%20expert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Duke%20of%20Sussex%20has%20also%20reportedly%20remained%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20his%20paternal%20cousin%2C%20Princess%20Beatrice%2C%20who%20may%20hold%20the%20key%20to%20%26quot%3Binitiating%20peace%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20ongoing%20feud%20between%20Harry%20and%20William%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20palace%20staffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725773820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3okahaj8_prince-harry_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fquietly-behind-scenes-prince-harry-secretly-in-contact-with-royal-family-6516545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prince%20Harry%20was%20recently%20spotted%20attending%20the%20funeral%20of%20Lord%20Robert%20Fellowes%2C%2