ensky%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20spoke%20to%20President%20Putin%20over%20the%20phone%20on%20August%2027.%20A%20Russian%20Embassy%20statement%20said%20that%20during%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20informed%20President%20Putin%20about%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Kiev%20and%20stressed%20India's%20commitment%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20settlement%20for%20Ukraine%20by%20political%20and%20diplomatic%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20it%20was%20during%20this%20phone%20call%20that%20the%20leaders%20decided%20that%20NSA%20Doval%20would%20travel%20to%20Moscow%20for%20peace%20talks.%20No%20details%20regarding%20the%20schedule%20of%20this%20visit%20are%20currently%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVladimir%20Putin%20shared%20his%20principled%20assessment%20of%20the%20destructive%20policies%20of%20the%20Kiev%20authorities%20and%20their%20Western%20patrons%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20highlight%20Russia's%20approaches%20to%20resolving%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20Embassy%20said%20about%20the%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20said%20the%20two%20leaders%20exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PM%20shared%20insights%20from%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ukraine.%20He%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20as%20well%20as%20sincere%20and%20practical%20engagement%20between%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20achieve%20an%20abiding%20and%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PMO%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20reiterated%20India's%20firm%20commitment%20to%20support%20an%20%26quot%3Bearly%2C%20abiding%20and%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20official%20handle%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20met%20its%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%20During%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20discussed%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20was%20never%20neutral%2C%20we%20have%20always%20been%20on%20the%20side%20of%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%20has%20named%20India%20among%20the%20three%20countries%20Russia%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20our%20friends%20and%20partners%2C%20who%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20sincerely%20seek%20to%20resolve%20all%20issues%20surrounding%20this%20conflict%2C%20primarily%20China%2C%20Brazil%20and%20India.%20I%20constantly%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20colleagues%20on%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20world%20leaders%2C%20too%2C%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20India%20can%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20finding%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20yesterday%20held%20talks%20with%20Ukraine%20President%20Zelensky.%20%26quot%3BChina%20and%20India%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20resolving%20the%20conflict.%20What%20must%20not%20happen%20is%20to%20think%20that%20the%20conflict%20can%20be%20resolved%20by%20abandoning%20Ukraine%20to%20its%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20in%20Italian%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20sharply%20divided%20the%20world%20and%20most%20global%20powers%20have%20taken%20sides.%20New%20Delhi%2C%20however%2C%20has%20constantly%20called%20for%20peace%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20stressing%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20travelled%20to%20Russia%20in%20July%20and%20hugged%20President%20Putin%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20had%20referred%20to%20a%20Russian%20missile%20strike%20that%20killed%2037%20people%2C%20three%20of%20them%20children.%20He%20had%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20devastating%20blow%20to%20peace%20efforts%20to%20see%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%20hug%20the%20world's%20most%20bloody%20criminal%20in%20Moscow%20on%20such%20a%20day%26quot%3B.%20On%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20embraced%20President%20Zelensky%20and%20the%20Ukraine%20leader%20said%20he%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20%26quot%3Bhonoured%20the%20memory%20of%20children%20whose%20lives%20were%20taken%20by%20Russian%20aggression%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BChildren%20of%20every%20country%20deserve%20to%20be%20safe.%20We%20must%20make%20it%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725771480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F6qdv2uv_modi-ukraine-putin_625x300_08_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-to-visit-moscow-for-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-sources-6516112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20will%20be%20travelling%20to%20Moscow%20this%20week%20to%20hold%20discussions%20aimed%20at%20resolving%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-to-visit-moscow-for-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-sources-6516112%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stree%202%20becomes%204th%20biggest%20Hindi%20film%20ever%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725770989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113161791%2Cimgsize-86406.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fshraddha-kapoor-rajkummar-raos-stree-2-beats-prabhas-baahubali-2-to-become-4th-biggest-hindi-film-ever%2Farticleshow%2F113161793.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left