s%20and%20cultures%20at%20the%20university%2C%20her%20family%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20late%20on%20Friday%20that%20was%20shared%20by%20the%20pro-Palestinian%20organization%20Institute%20of%20Middle%20East%20Understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20its%20troops%20had%20fired%20toward%20a%20male%20%26quot%3Bmain%20instigator%26quot%3B%20who%20posed%20a%20threat%20by%20hurling%20rocks%20at%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20was%20looking%20into%20reports%20that%20a%20female%20foreign%20national%20%26quot%3Bwas%20killed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20shots%20fired%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20the%20circumstances%20in%20which%20she%20was%20hit%20are%20under%20review.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20on%20the%20incident%20from%20Netanyahu's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFouad%20Nafaa%2C%20head%20of%20Rafidia%20Hospital%20in%20Nablus%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Eygi%20had%20arrived%20there%20in%20critical%20condition%20with%20a%20serious%20head%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20to%20perform%20a%20resuscitation%20operation%20on%20her%2C%20but%20unfortunately%20she%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Authority's%20official%20news%20agency%2C%20WAFA%2C%20said%20the%20incident%20occurred%20during%20a%20regular%20protest%20march%20by%20activists%20in%20Beita%2C%20a%20village%20near%20Nablus%20that%20has%20seen%20repeated%20attacks%20on%20Palestinians%20by%20Jewish%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEygi's%20family%20described%20her%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfiercely%20passionate%20human%20rights%20activist%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20recently%20participated%20in%20college%20campus%20protests%20against%20U.S.%20support%20for%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20statement%20called%20on%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20to%20pursue%20an%20independent%20U.S.%20probe%20into%20her%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20begged%20her%20not%20to%20go%20(to%20the%20West%20Bank)%2C%20but%20she%20had%20this%20deep%20conviction%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tradition%20of%20bearing%20witness%20to%20the%20oppression%20of%20people%20and%20their%20dignified%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20Aria%20Fani%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20Middle%20Eastern%20languages%20and%20cultures%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington%2C%20told%20the%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20president%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAysenur%20was%20a%20peer%20mentor%20in%20psychology%20who%20helped%20welcome%20new%20students%20to%20the%20department%20and%20provided%20a%20positive%20influence%20in%20their%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'DEEPLY%20DISTURBED'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House's%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20Sean%20Savett%20said%20Washington%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20an%20American%20citizen%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Israel%20to%20ask%20for%20more%20information%20and%20request%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20Savett%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Senator%20Chris%20Van%20Hollen%20said%20Eygi%20was%20the%20third%20American%20killed%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20sparked%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20a%20resurgence%20of%20West%20Bank%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BBiden%20Administration%20has%20not%20been%20doing%20enough%20to%20pursue%20justice%20and%20accountability%20on%20their%20behalf%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Van%20Hollen%2C%20a%20Democrat%20like%20Biden%20and%20Harris%2C%20who%20sits%20on%20the%20Senate's%20Foreign%20Relations%20Committee.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Netanyahu%20Government%20will%20not%20purs