id%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20leave%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20to%20this%20government.%20The%20current%20national%20anthem%20we%20have%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20existence%20of%20our%20independent%20Bangladesh.%20It%20reflects%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Bengal%20partition%20and%20the%20merging%20of%20the%20two%20Bengals.%20How%20can%20an%20anthem%20created%20to%20unite%20the%20two%20Bengals%20become%20the%20national%20anthem%20of%20an%20independent%20Bangladesh%3F%20This%20anthem%20was%20imposed%20on%20us%20by%20India%20in%201971.%20Many%20songs%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20national%20anthem.%20The%20government%20should%20form%20a%20new%20commission%20to%20select%20a%20new%20national%20anthem.%26quot%3B%20Hossain%20said%20Bangladesh%2C%20as%20a%20neighbouring%20country%2C%20wants%20a%20friendly%20relationship%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20heard%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20our%20cricket%20team%20in%20India.%20Since%20the%20Bangladesh%20Cricket%20Board%20(BCB)%20is%20in%20charge%2C%20they%20will%20decide%20on%20the%20necessary%20course%20of%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhaka%20Tribune%20quoted%20the%20advisor%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20attacks%20on%20mosques%2C%20temples%2C%20and%20shrines%20as%20%26quot%3Bheinous%26quot%3B%2C%20Hossain%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20attack%20places%20of%20worship%20are%20enemies%20of%20humanity.%20They%20are%20criminals%2C%20and%20they%20will%20be%20prosecuted%20under%20existing%20laws.%E2%80%9D%20Hossain%20further%20said%20local%20citizens%20as%20well%20as%20madrasa%20students%20will%20guard%20temples%20during%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20to%20prevent%20any%20attack%20or%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadrasa%20students%20were%20never%20involved%20in%20terrorism.%20That%20was%20propaganda%20and%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20previous%20government.%E2%80%9DThe%20advisor%20said%20that%20after%20the%20change%20in%20government%2C%20there%20had%20been%20attacks%20on%20the%20houses%20of%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20just%20as%20Muslim%20houses%20were%20attacked%20and%20this%20should%20not%20be%20viewed%20differently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725763560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj4vjvr9g_muhammad-yunus-afp_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-advisor-says-no-plan-to-change-bangladeshs-national-anthem-6514120%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20plan%20to%20change%20the%20national%20anthem%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20country's%20Religious%20Affairs%20Advisor%20AFM%20Khalid%20Hossain%20said%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-advisor-says-no-plan-to-change-bangladeshs-national-anthem-6514120%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20believes%20Iran%20has%20transferred%20short-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20to%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725763498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113160534%2Cimgsize-522131.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia%2Farticleshow%2F113160521.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113160521.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20believes%20Iran%20has%20transferred%20short-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20to%20Russia%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20escalating%20conflict%20and%20European%20security%20t