ing%20this%20time%3A%20Krishna%20made%20peace%20with%20his%20height%20and%20discovered%20para-badminton.%20When%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20coach%20explained%20that%20there%20was%20a%20category%20in%20para-badminton%20that%20allowed%20for%20international%20competition%2C%20it%20was%20a%20game-changer%20for%20him.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20never%20looked%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20training%20under%20Gaurav%20Khanna%2C%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20para-badminton%20team%20and%20a%20Dronacharya%20awardee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20competing%20internationally%2C%20earning%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%202018%20Asian%20Para%20Games%20and%20the%20World%20Para%20Badminton%20Championships%20in%202019.%20His%20defining%20moment%20came%20with%20winning%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20singles%20SH6%20category%20at%20the%20Tokyo%202020%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20handling%20nerves%20at%20such%20big-stakes%20competitions%2C%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3ESportstar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20being%20calm.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20times%20it%20happens%20that%20when%20you%20are%20playing%20such%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20how%20you%20can%20control%20yourself%2C%20your%20emotions%3B%20that%20becomes%20more%20important.%20When%20you%20come%20into%20such%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20you%20have%20to%20stay%20a%20little%20calm%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20celebrated%20his%20triumph%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20major%20blow%20when%20his%20mother%20passed%20away%20six%20months%20after%20his%20victory.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20too%20many%20hurdles%20after%20her%20passing%20away.%20She%20was%20my%20everything.%20But%20then%20my%20mental%20situation%20worsened%20after%20her%20death.%20I%20sunk%20into%20darkness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20friends%20and%20badminton%20helped%20pull%20him%20away%20from%20the%20dark%20place.%20He%20decided%20to%20do%20his%20best%20and%20started%20working%20on%20defending%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337854%2Fsheetal-devi-arjuna-award-para-archery-first-armless-female-archer-jammu-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParalympic%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20are%20on%20Krishna%20as%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20potential%20repeat%20of%20his%20Tokyo%20success%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Folympics%2Fparis-paralympics-2024%2Fnews%2Fparis-paralympics-2024-krishna-nagar-gold-medal-defence-badminton-indian-athletes%2Farticle68562213.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Paris%202024%3A%20With%20one%20eye%20on%20defending%20Paralympics%20title%2C%20Krishna%20Nagar%20banks%20on%20tight-knit%20Indian%20contingent%20for%20support%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20Aditya%20Padinjat%2C%20Published%20on%2024%20August%202024%2C%20Courtesy%20Sportstar%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fsport%2Fother%2F2021%2FSep%2F05%2Fkrishna-nagar-wins-gold-in-mens-badminton-singles-sh6-class-at-tokyo-paralympics-2354582.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Once%20bullied%20for%20short%20stature%2C%20Krishna%20Nagar%20wins%20gold%20in%20men%E2%80%99s%20badminton%20singles%20at%20Tokyo%20Paralympics%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EPublished%20on%206%20September%202021%2C%20Courtesy%20The%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724937